    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26991777_67_14712-14758",
      "chapterUid": 67,
      "range": "14712-14758",
      "markText": "但割了几下只在大腿上割出一道伤痕，她情急之中一咬牙剁下自己的两截手指作药引，扔进药煲中熬药。",
      "totalCount": 289,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26991777&chapterUid=67&rangeStart=14712&rangeEnd=14758",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00632020719bdca10068da5?chapterUid=67&rangeStart=14712&rangeEnd=14758"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26991777_67_10613-10667",
      "chapterUid": 67,
      "range": "10613-10667",
      "markText": "袁世凯从小就随嗣父出入官场，耳濡目染，轻车熟路，办起事情来游刃有余，而且人情练达、机敏周密，深得同事的赞扬。",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26991777&chapterUid=67&rangeStart=10613&rangeEnd=10667",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00632020719bdca10068da5?chapterUid=67&rangeStart=10613&rangeEnd=10667"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26991777_68_13717-13802",
      "chapterUid": 68,
      "range": "13717-13802",
      "markText": "稽查军纪是个良心活，你上心，就天天忙，不上心，你窝在屋里睡觉也没人管；如果上心，便可借机学到不少东西，不上心，便是虚度光阴，一无所长。我还是那句话，长不长出息，看你自己。",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26991777&chapterUid=68&rangeStart=13717&rangeEnd=13802",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00632020719bdca10068da5?chapterUid=68&rangeStart=13717&rangeEnd=13802"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26991777_86_1486-1549",
      "chapterUid": 86,
      "range": "1486-1549",
      "markText": "正月中旬，北洋海军提督丁汝昌、定远舰管带刘步蟾、镇远舰管带林泰曾及继任管带杨用霖自杀身亡，大量战舰被日军俘获，补充到日本海军。",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26991777&chapterUid=86&rangeStart=1486&rangeEnd=1549",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00632020719bdca10068da5?chapterUid=86&rangeStart=1486&rangeEnd=1549"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26991777_71_913-992",
      "chapterUid": 71,
      "range": "913-992",
      "markText": "忍让，办外交讲的是“和为贵”，能不战就不战，因为中国积贫积弱太久，需要争取几十年的和平来追赶列国。他常用的外交手段是“以夷制夷”，遇事请列国调停，避免发生战事",
      "totalCount": 240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26991777&chapterUid=71&rangeStart=913&rangeEnd=992",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00632020719bdca10068da5?chapterUid=71&rangeStart=913&rangeEnd=992"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26991777_67_24413-24457",
      "chapterUid": 67,
      "range": "24413-24457",
      "markText": "我们这些人只有靠做事换顶戴，机遇好换红顶子，机遇不佳费力不讨好也没处诉冤，也不必戚戚。”",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26991777&chapterUid=67&rangeStart=24413&rangeEnd=24457",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00632020719bdca10068da5?chapterUid=67&rangeStart=24413&rangeEnd=24457"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26991777_91_22711-22780",
      "chapterUid": 91,
      "range": "22711-22780",
      "markText": "谭嗣同本来有机会与梁启超一起逃走，但他却道：“各国变法无不以流血而成，今日中国未闻有因变法而流血者，此国之所以不昌也。有之，则自嗣同始。”",
      "totalCount": 225,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26991777&chapterUid=91&rangeStart=22711&rangeEnd=22780",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00632020719bdca10068da5?chapterUid=91&rangeStart=22711&rangeEnd=22780"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26991777_67_1128-1190",
      "chapterUid": 67,
      "range": "1128-1190",
      "markText": "此外还有为良家妇女苟且提供方便的台基、专为侍候洋人的咸水妹，还有苦力、脚夫等人光顾的最低等的“钉棚”，此处则连妓院也称不上。",
      "totalCount": 224,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26991777&chapterUid=67&rangeStart=1128&rangeEnd=1190",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00632020719bdca10068da5?chapterUid=67&rangeStart=1128&rangeEnd=1190"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26991777_67_591-655",
      "chapterUid": 67,
      "range": "591-655",
      "markText": "太平军禁娼，苏州、常州的烟花女子纷纷投奔上海，高张艳帜。租界工部局认为娼妓业既能创一笔可观的税收，又可吸引人气，因此也大力支持。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26991777&chapterUid=67&rangeStart=591&rangeEnd=655",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00632020719bdca10068da5?chapterUid=67&rangeStart=591&rangeEnd=655"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26991777_67_6689-6770",
      "chapterUid": 67,
      "range": "6689-6770",
      "markText": "四哥这就见外了，你如果是耍赖的人，写了借据又有何用？如果四哥是一诺千金之人，没有借据又何妨？而且我说过了，我不要四哥还钱，只要四哥将来记得这份交情，别忘了兄弟。”",
      "totalCount": 210,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26991777&chapterUid=67&rangeStart=6689&rangeEnd=6770",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00632020719bdca10068da5?chapterUid=67&rangeStart=6689&rangeEnd=6770"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26991777_67_467-526",
      "chapterUid": 67,
      "range": "467-526",
      "markText": "上海的烟花柳巷是随着开埠而繁荣起来的。尤其是太平军定鼎金陵，东克苏常，南破杭州后，苏浙一带的富户巨室无不携款奔赴上海。",
      "totalCount": 198,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26991777&chapterUid=67&rangeStart=467&rangeEnd=526",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/00632020719bdca10068da5?chapterUid=67&rangeStart=467&rangeEnd=526"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26991777_67_8604-8634",
      "chapterUid": 67,
      "range": "8604-8634",
